eErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"e144c74d-b449-4c94-ac64-568bbc3be501","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"85d24e9d-ec64-44ea-ba06-329fdb465c76","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"7af3bcaf-94eb-4cfb-b79d-6a302e9a806d","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5157,1420],"id":"15cb75ad-fdeb-4962-8d0e-576ec4971768","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#social","cachedResultName":"#social"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5481,1420],"id":"27db272b-d708-42df-8a44-a7c40a905494","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Daily Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — daily at 9:00. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Post","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"93795f22-a11c-d5e7-ac73-9bf9dc922ba2","name":"Note: Daily Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Post\n\nShapes the item: writes `postId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"7a1e3eac-5e75-d0ec-536d-afeaf77aed9d","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Post"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.postId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Detect Sentiment · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"0ae903bc-4928-af77-2086-7820a031723d","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"508d6b13-1590-ada7-ba70-a553ae12d0ce","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Detect Sentiment\n\nScores the text's sentiment; ports fire positive / neutral / negative.\n\nPorts: ①→ Escalate Negative — Slack · ②→ Log Neutral Feedback, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Thank the Sender\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"5fca29fc-e049-877b-e4d0-76e4a3ec4de9","name":"Note: Detect Sentiment"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Detect Sentiment** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"bd1f1c80-3221-360f-d192-48a91b97d486","name":"Note: Anthropic Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Negative — Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Collect All Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,40],"id":"88652edb-40b9-f993-aa34-aafcd8c1d528","name":"Note: Escalate Negative — Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Neutral Feedback\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Collect All Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,520],"id":"bd513232-6284-fa88-0187-eedb1b09e8a2","name":"Note: Log Neutral Feedback"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Thank the Sender\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Collect All Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,1000],"id":"b045508f-3827-6c12-2b7f-9508a76fe96f","name":"Note: Thank the Sender"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Collect All Outcomes\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Sort Posts Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"92706941-f45f-6953-652c-c4506265aeb2","name":"Note: Collect All Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Posts Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"15d84540-5d64-8a72-6681-c19a4c0e0f9a","name":"Note: Sort Posts Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"503b8806-fc00-ed88-b3f9-743cdc2b37eb","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 50 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"698a5a3c-0f3f-e970-3957-d3f5957e6a44","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"9b8d0476-a815-d24f-dde0-1367778d540d","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Telegram · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5421,520],"id":"1a9a9c5c-64f9-af36-89c4-4c6e0084457d","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Telegram\n\ntelegram — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Telegram bot token","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5745,520],"id":"7ffcc9f6-5a83-ddb1-b178-66ca49841fab","name":"Note: Send Summary to Telegram"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,1540],"id":"6c4ce78a-16b9-0072-4954-be3d45ffcefb","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5421,1540],"id":"a3ab4097-82b7-b957-1485-683f639fd4a9","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Monitor brand mentions with HTTP / REST API and Telegram 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Social Listening · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nMonitor brand mentions with HTTP / REST API and Telegram 24/7. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual engagement is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nDaily Schedule → Stamp & Shape Post → Payload Valid? → Detect Sentiment → Escalate Negative — Slack → Collect All Outcomes → Sort Posts Newest First → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to social listening without manual effort\n- Anyone automating engagement in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Anthropic API key; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"225d3eba-7235-581b-df57-31fb3c56bd5d","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"0396ba2b-31d8-ebe2-7808-1b279c12a311","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"9ce9695f-30b8-ceb8-168c-c3124aeb75e6","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your engagement process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"ef014f47-def5-e4e2-6324-af6a4f687353","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Daily Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Post","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Post":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Detect Sentiment","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Anthropic Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Detect Sentiment","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Detect Sentiment":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Negative — Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Neutral Feedback","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Thank the Sender","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Negative — Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect All Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Log Neutral Feedback":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect All Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Thank the Sender":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect All Outcomes","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Collect All Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Posts Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Posts Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Telegram","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Telegram":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"c8046f04-1df1-451f-a35f-e88940b8491e","id":"FDX07061"}